item.title: US Stocks Picked
item.description: BMY (Bristol-Myers Squibb Company) Large Bristol Myers Squibb shows promising developments in targeted cancer treatments, CAR T cell immunotherapy, and schizophrenia drug innovation, but investors should be mindful of industry volatility and insider selling indicators. DIS (The Walt Disney Company) Mega Despite some challenges in adapting to changing viewing habits, Disney’s strong theme parks division and global collaboration efforts make it a promising investment in the entertainment and media industry.
